# Formula files land here, auto-generated by the cli-release workflow
# on every cli-v* tag. This .gitkeep makes the directory visible
# before any release happens — Homebrew taps' `brew tap` check
# tolerates an empty Formula/ but having it tracked gives the
# repo a "this is where formulas live" affordance for visitors.
#
# Remove this file once a real formula lives in this directory; the
# release workflow doesn't touch it either way.
